  "url": "https://projects.accesscomputing.uw.edu/au/before.html",
  "title": "Accessible University Demo Site - Inaccessible Version",
  "html": "<html><head>\n\t<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n\t<title>Accessible University Demo Site - Inaccessible Version</title>\n  <link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"images/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png\">\n  <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" href=\"images/favicon/favicon-32x32.png\">\n  <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"16x16\" href=\"images/favicon/favicon-16x16.png\">\n  <link href=\"styles/au-shared.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <link href=\"styles/main.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<link href=\"styles/before-main.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<link href=\"styles/before-menu.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<link href=\"styles/before-form.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<link href=\"styles/before-modal.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<link href=\"styles/before-carousel.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"scripts/before-menu.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"scripts/before-form.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"scripts/before-modal.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"scripts/before-carousel.js\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div id=\"content\">\n\n    <div id=\"banner\">\n      <img id=\"logo\" src=\"images/au123456789.gif\" alt=\"au123456789.gif\" width=\"441\" height=\"90\">\n      <nav id=\"AU-menu\" aria-label=\"Demo site menu\">\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"index.html\" data-nexui-ref=\"e1\">Home</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"before.html\" aria-current=\"page\" data-nexui-ref=\"e2\">Before</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"after.html\" data-nexui-ref=\"e3\">After</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"info.html\" data-nexui-ref=\"e4\">Info</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n    </div>\n\n    <ul id=\"menu\">\n      <li><a href=\"#\" data-nexui-ref=\"e5\">About</a>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=News\">News</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Governance\">Governance</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Diversity\">Diversity</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Contact%20Us\">Contact Us</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><a href=\"#\" data-nexui-ref=\"e6\">Academics</a>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Degree%20Programs\">Degree Programs</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=AU%20Faculty\">AU Faculty</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Distance%20Learning\">Distance Learning</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Libraries\">Libraries</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><a href=\"#\" data-nexui-ref=\"e7\">Admissions</a>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Undergraduate\">Undergraduate</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Graduate\">Graduate</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Tuition\">Tuition</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Financial%20Aid\">Financial Aid</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><a href=\"#\" data-nexui-ref=\"e8\">Visitors</a>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Events\">Events</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Campus_Map\">Campus Map</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"somepage.html?ref=Parking\">Parking</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <div id=\"main\">\n\n      <div id=\"carousel\">\n        <div id=\"controls\">\n          <div id=\"btn-prev\"></div>\n          <div id=\"btn-next\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"slides\">\n          <div class=\"slide current\">\n            <img src=\"images/carousel/slide1.jpg\">\n            <div class=\"caption\">A modern shool</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"slide\">\n            <img src=\"images/carousel/slide2.jpg\">\n            <div class=\"caption\">rooted in its history</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"slide\">\n            <img src=\"images/carousel/slide3.jpg\">\n            <div class=\"caption\">with opportunities to learn</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"slide\">\n            <img src=\"images/carousel/slide4.jpg\">\n            <div class=\"caption\">and grow.</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      <ul class=\"lentils\"><li data-slide=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li><li data-slide=\"1\"></li><li data-slide=\"2\"></li><li data-slide=\"3\"></li></ul></div>\n\n      <div class=\"heading\">Welcome!</div>\n      <p>Accessible University (AU) is a fictional university, and this is its\n        fictional home page. This page is designed to demonstrate a variety of\n        common web design problems that result in visitors with disabilities\n        being unable to access the content or features of a web page.\n        Although the heading at the top of this section of the page\n        suggests that AU may be a welcoming institution,\n        the inaccessible design of this page sends the opposite message.\n      </p>\n\n      <img class=\"hr\" src=\"images/line_gradient.gif\" alt=\"horizontal line graphic\">\n\n      <div class=\"heading\">Bienvenido!</div>\n      <p>Accesible Universidad (UA) es una universidad ficticia, y esta es su\n        página de ficción. Esta página está diseñada para demostrar una variedad de\n        común de diseño web que se traducen en problemas de los visitantes con discapacidad\n        no poder acceder al contenido o las características de una página web.\n        Aunque el título en la parte superior de esta sección de la página\n        sugiere que AU puede ser una institución de bienvenida,\n        el diseño inaccesible de esta página envía el mensaje opuesto.\n      </p>\n\n      <img class=\"hr\" src=\"images/line_gradient.gif\" alt=\"horizontal line graphic\">\n\n      <div class=\"heading\">Can you spot the barriers?</div>\n      <p>There are at least 22 accessibility issues on this page.\n        To see a list of all known issues, <a href=\"info.html\" data-nexui-ref=\"e9\">click here</a>.\n        To see a more accessible version of this same page, <a href=\"after.html\" data-nexui-ref=\"e10\">click here</a>.\n        For a cheat sheet of accessibility issues, <a href=\"cheatsheet.html\" data-nexui-ref=\"e11\">click here</a>.\n      </p>\n\n      <img class=\"hr\" src=\"images/line_gradient.gif\" alt=\"horizontal line graphic\">\n\n      <div class=\"heading\">AU Enrollment Trends</div>\n      <table id=\"enrollment\">\n        <tbody><tr>\n          <td class=\"corner\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:6em\"></td>\n          <td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Last Year</b></td>\n          <td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>This Year</b></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><b>CS</b></td>\n          <td><b>Eng</b></td>\n          <td><b>Eco</b></td>\n          <td><b>Phy</b></td>\n          <td><b>Psy</b></td>\n          <td><b>CS</b></td>\n          <td><b>Eng</b></td>\n          <td><b>Eco</b></td>\n          <td><b>Phy</b></td>\n          <td><b>Psy</b></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><b>Undergraduate</b></td>\n          <!--Last Year-->\n          <td>1481</td>\n          <td>400</td>\n          <td>727</td>\n          <td>747</td>\n          <td>1006</td>\n          <!--This Year-->\n          <td>1500</td><!-- CS enrollment is the most popular, and climbing -->\n          <td>340</td><!-- English enrollment is dropping -->\n          <td>777</td><!-- Economics enrollment is climbing -->\n          <td>787</td><!-- Physics is growing steadily -->\n          <td>1112</td><!-- Psychology is climbing -->\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><b>Graduate</b></td>\n          <!--Last Year-->\n          <td>310</td>\n          <td>84</td>\n          <td>273</td>\n          <td>69</td>\n          <td>312</td>\n          <!--This Year-->\n          <td>350</td><!-- CS capped at maximum enrollment-->\n          <td>64</td><!-- waining interest in graduate studies in English -->\n          <td>341</td><!-- solid growth in Economics / business -->\n          <td>72</td><!-- slight increase in Physics -->\n          <td>325</td><!-- strong, slightly growing psych program -->\n        </tr>\n      </tbody></table>\n\n      <img class=\"hr\" src=\"images/line_gradient.gif\" alt=\"horizontal line graphic\">\n\n      <div class=\"heading\">AU Video</div>\n      <video src=\"video/au-promo.mp4\" poster=\"video/au-promo.jpg\" controls=\"\"></video>\n\n    </div><!--end #main-->\n\n    <div id=\"appForm\">\n\n      <div class=\"heading\">Apply Now!</div>\n        <p class=\"required reqExample\">(required fields are in blue)</p>\n\n      <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n\n        <!-- container for displaying form errors -->\n        <div id=\"error\"></div>\n\n        <div class=\"required\">\n          Name:\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" data-nexui-ref=\"e12\">\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"required\">\n          Email:\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"email\" data-nexui-ref=\"e13\">\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n          Country:\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"country\" data-nexui-ref=\"e14\">\n        </div>\n\n        <div><b>Desired major(s):</b></div>\n\n        <div id=\"majors\">\n          <div class=\"major\">Computer Science <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"major_cs\" data-nexui-ref=\"e15\"></div>\n          <div class=\"major\">Engineering <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"major_eng\" data-nexui-ref=\"e16\"></div>\n          <div class=\"major\">Economics <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"major_econ\" data-nexui-ref=\"e17\"></div>\n          <div class=\"major\">Physics <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"major_phy\" data-nexui-ref=\"e18\"></div>\n          <div class=\"major\">Psychology <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"major_psy\" data-nexui-ref=\"e19\"></div>\n          <div class=\"major\">Spanish <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"major_sp\" data-nexui-ref=\"e20\"></div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"captcha\">\n          <b>Security Test</b>\n          <p>Please enter the two words you see below, separated by a space</p>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"captcha\" data-nexui-ref=\"e21\">\n          <img src=\"images/captcha.png\">\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n          <input id=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" name=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" data-nexui-ref=\"e22\">\n        </div>\n\n      </form>\n\n    </div><!--end #sidebar-->\n\n    <div id=\"footer\">\n      <footer>\n        <div id=\"license\">\n          <div id=\"ccLogo\">    \n            <a rel=\"license\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" data-nexui-ref=\"e23\"><img alt=\"Creative Commons License\" style=\"border-width:0\" src=\"https://i.creativecommons.org/l/by-nc-sa/4.0/88x31.png\"></a>\n          </div>\n          <span xmlns:dct=\"http://purl.org/dc/terms/\" property=\"dct:title\">Accessible University</span> by <a xmlns:cc=\"http://creativecommons.org/ns#\" href=\"http://washington.edu/accesscomputing/AU\" property=\"cc:attributionName\" rel=\"cc:attributionURL\" data-nexui-ref=\"e24\">University of Washington</a> is licensed under a <a rel=\"license\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" data-nexui-ref=\"e25\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License</a>.\n        </div>\n        <p>This product was originally developed with support from the National Institute on Disability and Rehabilitation Research of the U.S. Department of Education (grant #H133D010306), and has been subsequently updated and maintained with support from the National Science Foundation (grants #CNS-0540615, CNS-0837508, CNS-1042260, CNS-1539179, and CNS-2137312). The contents do not necessarily represent the policies of the U.S. federal government, and you should not assume their endorsement.</p>\n      </footer>\n    </div>      \n\n  </div><!--end #content-->\n\n  <!--containers for displaying modal content-->\n  <div id=\"modalMask\"></div>\n  <div id=\"modalContent\">\n    <div class=\"modalHeading\">Accessibility Issues</div>\n    <button type=\"button\" id=\"modalClose\">x</button>\n    <ol>\n      <!-- Structure -->\n      <li>Missing landmark regions</li>\n      <li>No headings</li>\n      <li>Language not specified</li>\n      <!-- Images -->\n      <li>No alternate text on informative images</li>\n      <li>Missing or excessive alternate text on decorative images</li>\n      <!-- Color-->\n      <li>Insufficient color contrast</li>\n      <li>Color used to communicate information</li>\n      <!-- Keyboard-->\n      <li>Inaccessible keyboard interface</li>\n      <li>No visible indication of focus</li>\n      <li>No \"skip to main content\" link</li>\n      <!-- Links-->\n      <li>Redundant, uninformative link text</li>\n      <li>Links vs buttons</li>\n      <!-- Features -->\n      <li>Inaccessible navigation menu</li>\n      <li>Inaccessible carousel</li>\n      <li>Inaccessible modal dialog</li>\n      <!-- Forms -->\n      <li>Form not properly labeled</li>\n      <li>Inaccessible CAPTCHA</li>\n      <li>Inaccessible input validation</li>\n      <!-- Tables -->\n      <li>Missing accessible table markup</li>\n      <li>Missing abbreviation tags</li>\n      <!-- Video -->\n      <li>Inaccessible audio content in video</li>\n      <li>Inaccessible visual content in video</li> \n    </ol>\n    <button type=\"button\" id=\"modalOk\">OK</button>\n  </div>\n\n\n</body></html>"
}
